{
  "description": "A vibrant nighttime scene captures a fireworks display over a body of water, with a prominent bridge and city skyline in the background. The fireworks explode in a brilliant white and gold display, resembling a large flower or bloom. The bridge, lit with rows of white and orange lights, stretches across the dark water, leading towards a cityscape filled with illuminated buildings. The city skyline features a mix of high-rise buildings, their windows glowing with yellow and white light, creating a sense of urban density and activity. The overall composition balances the natural spectacle of the fireworks with the man-made structures of the bridge and city. The dark water reflects some of the lights, adding depth and visual interest to the image.",
